race.comment: SPINHOF (4) didn't handle the wet track at Horsham, but brought strong form to that. Best figures measure up nicely, and he will take plenty of beating. Goes on top of GOLD GOVERNOR (1) who gave away a big start at Stawell and never a winning threat from there. Was in need of the run regardless. Has an inside gate today and with the extra fitness he also rates a chance. PAINT ME RED (3) peaks and has a key gear switch. Tumbles in grade and has the ability. Will get every chance from an inside barrier. NICKING GRACIE (7) will be around the mark. Looks the pick of the rest.
